    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-09-10T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-09-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="568" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d568">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Terrell</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-09-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 10,
                                    1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your telegrams 6th and 9th received. Mooradian’s surrender to you
                            obviates judicial question. If he assents you may send him away as
                            indicated, otherwise forcible deportation could only be performed by
                            Turkish authority.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
